OL,3,CSecond boy charged with attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of 14-year-old
OL,6,FA second boy has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder after a 14-year-old
OL,8,Fwas stabbed outside shops in Sheffield.
OL,10,FThe 17-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,11,Ffor legal reasons, will appear at
OL,12,FSheffield Magistrates' Court on Friday
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident in Market
OL,14,FSquare, Woodhouse, shortly before 10pm
OL,15,Fon 18 March.
OL,17,FAnother boy of the same age has
OL,18,Falready appeared in court charged with
OL,19,Fattempted murder and was given bail to
OL,20,Fappear at Sheffield Crown Court next
OL,21,Fmonth.
