OL,3,CSecond boy charged with attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of 14-year-old
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,7,Fvictim, who was taken to hospital with
OL,8,Flife-threatening injuries, has since
OL,9,Fstabilised and is recovering well.
OL,11,FThe incident, which was the latest
OL,12,Fknife crime involving young people in
OL,13,FSheffield, prompted Ch Supt Jamie
OL,14,FHenderson to speak out about the
OL,15,F"growing disregard for human life" in
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire.
OL,18,FSpeaking the following day he said:
OL,19,F"This is senseless, it is devastating,
OL,20,Fand it is utterly unacceptable.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
