OL,6,F"A child's life was brought to the
OL,7,Fbrink over a moment of violence that
OL,8,Fshould never have happened.
OL,10,F"Behind every incident like this is a
OL,11,Ftrail of trauma with families
OL,12,Fshattered, communities shaken and
OL,13,Ffutures potentially destroyed."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
